  "text": "It is easy to calculate the empirical mean value from data counts. Consequently, all that is required is to calculate the value α • in order to figure out the value of parameter α. This can be done using the second moment (variance) value. Variance of one dimension is enough to calculate α • [CITATION_1] :",
